309
00:19:34,852 --> 00:19:36,061
Meu Deus...

310
00:19:41,942 --> 00:19:43,027
Meu Deus!

311
00:19:47,489 --> 00:19:51,202
Ouve, isto nunca aconteceu.
Entendido?

312
00:19:54,746 --> 00:19:57,208
