Discuti com a Bernadette.

322
00:20:28,738 --> 00:20:29,865
Porquê?

323
00:20:30,032 --> 00:20:31,909
Deu-me um relógio lindo.

324
00:20:35,328 --> 00:20:37,122
Leonard, entendes isto?

325
00:20:37,832 --> 00:20:38,833
Sim...

326
00:20:38,999 --> 00:20:40,000
Fala com ele.

327
00:20:49,509 --> 00:20:50,510
Bolas.

328
00:20:52,345 --> 00:20:53,763
